rows.label: tlk41700126_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Yo, we meet again. Are you getting
good use out of that Perfect Range Sensor
I gave you?

rows.label: tlk41700126_01_msg0003
rows.name: I've been traveling all over Alst.

rows.label: tlk41700126_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Observing plants from all over and
continuing my research day by day.

rows.label: tlk41700126_01_msg0005
rows.name:
I've finished the first leg, so I've come back
to my hometown like this.

rows.label: tlk41700126_01_msg0006
rows.name:
Fieldwork is fun, but writing the thesis
is a bit of a pain...

rows.label: tlk41700126_01_msg0007
rows.name: But I've got to pull it together somehow.
